These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: zucchini, garlic, radish
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, manager, musician
1. the person eating zucchini is in an even position##4
2. the project-manager is on the left or right of the musician##3
3. the project-manager is the person eating garlic##1
4. the person eating radish is on the far left##1
5. the manager is the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | radish | zucchini | garlic |
| Job    | manager    | musician | project-manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, trike, jet-ski
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person driving the trike is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | cooking | sudoku | collecting |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | trike     | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, filmmaking, card-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, jazz, soul
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | card-games     | filmmaking | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | reggae     | soul  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, comedy, zombie
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, snowboarding, rowing
1. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | comedy  | fantasy  |
| Sport         | soccer  | snowboarding | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, woodworking, dancing
There are 3 different nationalities: british, indonesian, egyptian
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the british##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
3. the egyptian is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | fishing   | dancing | woodworking    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | egyptian     | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, rock-climbing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, golf
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | rock-climbing | board-games   |
| Sport   | golf     | cycling    | sailing |

