.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, satire, sports
3 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, horse
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching drama movies is between the owner of the horse and the person watching sports movies##2
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | drama | satire |
| Pet           | rabbit         | snake         | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, tomato, raspberry
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, hamster
1. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating apricot##2
2. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | tomato | raspberry | apricot |
| Pet    | lizard    | hedgehog | hamster     |

