.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, house, reggae
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, surfing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | house  | jazz  |
| Sport         | volleyball | surfing | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, water, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: pear, kiwi, eggplant
1. the person eating pear is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | juice    | soy-milk      | water |
| Food       | kiwi | eggplant | pear   |

