The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, airplane, van
1. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the person driving the bike is the nurse##1
3. the person driving the van is the videographer##1
4. the videographer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | social-worker | videographer | nurse |
| Transport   | airplane | van   | bike |

