.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, indonesian, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, rugby, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the indonesian##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
