.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, chess
3 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, hedgehog
1. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | chess | collecting |
| Pet     | fish    | hedgehog  | guinea-pig   |

