1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | satire     | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | indie | funk    |

