.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, video-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, folk, reggae
1. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | video-games | board-games   | reading |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | house | reggae      |

