.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, lemonade
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, chinese, polish
1. the polish is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | coffee | juice | lemonade |
| Nationality   | chinese   | polish          | malaysian |

