.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, goat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, soccer, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | hedgehog  | goat   | mouse |
| Sport   | skateboarding | soccer | sailing       |

 